  R1-2021 (Iris) release version of the FOLIO platform, built from R1-2021 release artifacts, with all updates  [Iris release notes](https://wiki.folio.org/display/REL/R1+2021+%28Iris%29+Release+Notes). For details see http://localhost:3000/settings/about after `vagrant up`.
